Package: rcdkTools
Type: Package
Title: rcdkTools
Version: 0.3.2
Author: person("Eric", "Bach", email = "eric.bach@aalto.fi", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Eric Bach <eric.bach@aalto.fi>
Description: Set of wrappers around rcdk-package functions. For examples, this
    package performs atom configuration specific for each molecular fingerprint
    prior their calculation. Same holds for molecular descriptors. It also 
    provides functionality to store fingerprints and descriptors into a matrix,
    cvs-file respectively as json-file.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    data.table,
    fingerprint,
    igraph,
    rcdk (>= 3.4.9.2),
    tictoc,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
